## Step 2: Check for any additional capital contributions or withdrawals

- Additional investments from owners/shareholders

## Step 3: Determine the final paid-in capital value
Since there were no additional capital contributions or withdrawals during the period, the ending paid-in capital remains the same as the initial value: 13,000,000.00.
